    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Cubic zirconian weeks all around. I like that comparison because, although c.z. doesn&#8217;t shine like diamonds, it&#8217;s still pretty in a ridiculous kind of way. And most grumpy days are hardly without their sparkly sides. In fact, when things are bad, and there is no chocolate to wear, why not embrace the mediocrity and don some &#8220;pink ice&#8221; jewelry? Just the name &#8220;pink ice&#8221; is bound to be a mood enhancer, no?</p>
    </div>

